Package org.ddolib.common.dominance

package org.ddolib.common.dominance
This package contains the classes implementing dominance checkers.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.ddolib.common
    This package contains the interfaces and classes that can be needed for all kind of solvers
    org.ddolib.common.solver
    This package contains interfaces that must be extended to implements solvers.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    DefaultDominanceChecker<T>
    Default implementation of a DominanceChecker that performs no dominance checking.
    DominanceChecker<T>
    Object that, given a dominance, will check if a state is dominated.
    SimpleDominanceChecker<T>
    The SimpleDominanceChecker class implements a straightforward dominance management mechanism used in search algorithms based on Multi-valued Decision Diagrams (MDDs), such as DDO (Decision Diagram Optimization).
